(271, 'eBay live chat', 'ebay', 'eBay Live Chat | How Do I Get to Speak to Someone at Ebay', 'Easily contact eBay support through their live chat option. Learn how to shop and sell on eBay with these simple, step-by-step instructions. Get full details here.', 'eBay live chat', 'Etah Dolan is a seasoned tech blogger with over 8 years of experience in writing in-depth and engaging articles about the latest trends in technology. Having authored numerous articles on topics ranging from gadgets to software innovations, Etah is passionate about simplifying complex tech concepts for readers. His expertise lies in delivering insightful, easy-to-understand content that resonates with both tech enthusiasts and everyday users.', '<p style=\"color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-family: Cambria; font-size: 18px;\">eBay is an e-commerce platform that facilitates consumer-to-consumer and business-to-consumer sales. This platform is free to use for buyers, but sellers are charged fees for listing items after a limited number. eBay offers an&nbsp;<strong>ebay live chat&nbsp;</strong>to solve all the queries of its consumers. You can ask any questions to eBay they will provide the answers immediately. Their customer support is extremely fast. If you have any issues related to your order then contact them now.</p><h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"font-size: 22px; color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-family: Cambria;\">How do I live chat on eBay?</h2><p style=\"color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-family: Cambria; font-size: 18px;\">You can chat with email support by following these simple and easy steps:-</p><ul style=\"color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-family: Cambria; font-size: 18px;\"><li>First, on your ‘home’ page click on ‘Help &amp; Contact’ in the toolbar at the top of the page.</li><li>After that, a big blue box appears that says “How can we help you today?</li><li>Now you need to seek for the “search eBay help”</li><li>At last start typing “Contacting eBay Customer Services”</li><li>That will take you to the link contacting eBay Customer Service.</li><li>Click on the link then you will see the options, Call you, Call us, and Chat with us.</li></ul><h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"font-size: 21px; color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-family: Cambria;\">Does eBay still have live chat?</h3><p style=\"color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-family: Cambria; font-size: 18px;\">Once, eBay had a live chat option available at a stage but later disappeared in help pages and now eBay chat option is absolutely no longer to be had. Nowadays there is no link available for live chat, many customers tried for days and days by clicking contact eBay but there is no use. Even though it shows a chat option but it just takes you loading and gives you a phone number or an email link to&nbsp;<a href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20231001064413/https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/EBay\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\" style=\"color: rgb(84, 190, 115);\">eBay</a>. In this way, a chat option is not available right now at eBay.</p><h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"font-size: 20px; color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-family: Cambria;\">How can I speak to eBay?</h4><p style=\"color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-family: Cambria; font-size: 18px;\">If you have an issue with an item you just received or questions about selling items on eBay, you can contact to eBay customer support easily. You can contact its customer services by dialling its toll-free number. They have the answers of all your questions. You can also contact them through the “Help &amp; Contact” section on the official website of eBay. You can also contact them via Twitter or ask questions to the eBay customer support, but you can’t send an email for customer support.&nbsp;<strong>chat with ebay&nbsp;</strong>option is not available right now. So you can’t contact them through live chat.</p><h5 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"font-size: 19px; color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-family: Cambria;\">How can I get a call back from eBay?</h5><p style=\"color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-family: Cambria; font-size: 18px;\">Visit the official website of eBay and click on Customer Support at the very top of the page and then the Contact tab. After that, make a selection and the next page will have the call or be called options. Call eBay customer support to talk with an&nbsp;<strong>ebay chat expert</strong>. You have to call eBay to get the answers of your questions. To contact eBay, follow these simple steps:-</p><p style=\"color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-family: Cambria; font-size: 18px;\"><strong>Go to the official website of eBay and login to your account.</strong></p><ul style=\"color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-family: Cambria; font-size: 18px;\"><li>Click on Help&amp; Contact.</li><li>Now, click Contact Us.</li><li>Then choose the catogory such as, buying, selling, return, etc.</li><li>After choosing the category, choose your topic.</li><li>Now click on Subtopic.</li><li>At last, click on the contact option.</li></ul><h5 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"font-size: 19px; color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-family: Cambria;\">eBay live chat not working</h5><p style=\"color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-family: Cambria; font-size: 18px;\">The live chat option of eBay is completely unavailable now and the phone support button as disappeared. You still can contact eBay customer service support by dialing its toll-free number. Your eBay live chat option is not working because eBay defunct this option. Even there is no&nbsp;<strong>ebay chat link&nbsp;</strong>available for live chat, many customers tried for days and days by clicking contact eBay but there is no use. If you have a question or wish to contact eBay, you must go through their automated system. Click on “Contact Us” on its official website and the system is fairly easy to navigate. If you have questions about an eBay process or an eBay transaction, you can contact eBay customer support through its phone number. If the Help Centre of eBay failed to solve your problems then dial its phone number.</p><h5 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"font-size: 19px; color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-family: Cambria;\">How do I chat with eBay support?</h5><p style=\"color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-family: Cambria; font-size: 18px;\">You can’t find a live chat option on eBay because is it completely unavailable now. You can’t contact eBay customer support through the live chat option. There is no link available for a live chat on the official website of eBay. Even the links of the chat option disappeared. While eBay does not offer a live chat option, they do have a telephone number. You can get the details on the official website of eBay. In some cases,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20231001064413/https://teqsman.com/live-chat/ebay/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" style=\"color: rgb(84, 190, 115);\">contacting eBay</a>&nbsp;directly may not be your option. You can also solve your queries by going to eBay discussion board and eBay knowledge board. If your query is category-specific then you will get the proper help from the eBay discussion board. eBay knowledge board is also a type of eBay’s customer service system. This is easy to use and it is more helpful in many cases.</p><h5 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"font-size: 19px; color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-family: Cambria;\">How long does it take for eBay to respond?</h5><p style=\"color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-family: Cambria; font-size: 18px;\">eBay helps its customers to resolve all the problems. It generally responds immediately but in the case of a customer’s claim, its respond can take 30 days. If you want the answers of this question ”&nbsp;<strong>Is eBay Chat Safe?</strong>” they yes it is completely safe. But these days eBay closed its live chat option. If you have issues related to refunds and returns, problem with an order suspended account, want to report a seller, a fraudulent charge and other issues then you can contact eBay customer support by dialling its phone number. eBay also has on-line technical support, and a response is typically received within 24 hours. You can contact the online Helpdesk.&nbsp; Live chat option, Direct email option is disappeared from the ebay website. At one time it was also possible to contact eBay directly from your private account using a convenient address and to obtain a response. Contacting eBay customer support was so easy back then. Unfortunately now, it became more and more difficult to reach eBay quickly. It is force buyers and sellers to rely on self-help also an automated system also became unable to provide specific and immediate help.</p>', 'https://www.teqsman.com/storage/app/public/blog_images/rstcUp1hYy33rgwsvJ7rkuXnfaDOV0mowxWR9mAh.webp', NULL, 'live-chat', 'Ethan Dolan', '2024-09-17 12:33:10', '2024-09-17 12:33:10'),
(272, 'Comcast bill pay online steps', 'comcast', 'Comcast Bill Pay | Online Payment Tips and Suggestions', 'Easily manage your Comcast services online anytime. Simple bill payment, instant support, schedule appointments, and get answers 24/7.', 'Comcast bill pay', 'Etah Dolan is a seasoned tech blogger with over 8 years of experience in writing in-depth and engaging articles about the latest trends in technology. Having authored numerous articles on topics ranging from gadgets to software innovations, Etah is passionate about simplifying complex tech concepts for readers. His expertise lies in delivering insightful, easy-to-understand content that resonates with both tech enthusiasts and everyday users.', '<p style=\"color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-family: Cambria; font-size: 18px;\">Life is even easier for&nbsp;<strong>Comcast bill pay</strong>&nbsp;customers who want to pay for their TV, Internet or phone bills with cash.</p><p style=\"color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-family: Cambria; font-size: 18px;\">Comcast stated a new payment method for customers through a partnership with&nbsp;PayNearMe, this week, a new feature in the XFINITY My Account app that let customers pay their Comcast bills in cash at more than 7,700 participating 7-Eleven stores. Combined with more than 500 XFINITY stores, Comcast customers have access to more than 8,000 cash payment points in the US.</p><p style=\"color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-family: Cambria; font-size: 18px;\">With most 7-Eleven stores open 24/7; customers can now pay their bills 24/7 near their home.</p><p style=\"color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-family: Cambria; font-size: 18px;\"><strong>How it works:</strong></p><ul style=\"color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-family: Cambria; font-size: 18px;\"><li>In the XFINITY My Account app, go to the Pay Bill section and select the new option, Cash via PayNearMe.</li><li>Select the amount to pay to your convenient and follow the instructions until you receive a code.</li><li>Visit a participating 7-Eleven store nearby, scan the barcode on your phone and pay the selected amount.</li><li>7-Eleven will offer a paper delivery and users will receive a digital receipt on their phone confirming the payment amount.</li></ul><p style=\"color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-family: Cambria; font-size: 18px;\">“We have seen steady growth in the number and size of companies using PayNearMe to remotely withdraw cash,” said Christian Solomine, senior vice president of business and government at PayNearMe. “Customers keep telling us that they want to pay at convenient locations according to their own schedule and schedule.”</p><h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"font-size: 22px; color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-family: Cambria;\">Comcast Bill Payment</h2><p style=\"color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-family: Cambria; font-size: 18px;\">Use comcast Pay-bill directly as it is seen that comcast tv is one of the most demanding cable television in the world. You can easily use or pay the bill for your comcast tv.</p><p style=\"color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-family: Cambria; font-size: 18px;\">In the United States of America, Comcast tv is largely used as it is one of the most popular television networks. Charter Communications is the parent company that acquired the Time Warner Cable in 2016. Time Warner was the second largest cable network before the takeover. One of the main features of the service is that you have an online access account. You can manage many things and also use for Comcast Pay Bill.</p><p style=\"color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-family: Cambria; font-size: 18px;\">Paying for your Comcast bill has become very easy and straightforward thanks to the internet. All you need is a credit card and your online access account. We’ll show you how to pay your bill via the official account.</p><p style=\"color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-family: Cambria; font-size: 18px;\">The prerequisite is that you have an online account to pay your bill online.</p><h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"font-size: 21px; color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-family: Cambria;\">Comcast Bill Pay login&nbsp;steps</h3><p style=\"color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-family: Cambria; font-size: 18px;\">As mentioned earlier, customers can pay their bills through the official website by logging into their accounts. You can make a one-time payment or activate the automatic payment options so that you do not have to repeat this process every month. Below is a step-by-step guide to Comcast Bill Payment.</p><ul style=\"color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-family: Cambria; font-size: 18px;\"><li>Open the login portal here.</li><li>From the home screen, select “<strong>Pay bill</strong>“.</li><li>On the next screen, click&nbsp;<strong>Once</strong>.</li><li>You can use either a credit or a debit card to pay.</li><li>Select the payment method from the menu and click&nbsp;<strong>Next</strong>.</li><li>Enter your payment information and make the payment.</li></ul><p style=\"color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-family: Cambria; font-size: 18px;\">So you can pay for your Bill of Comcast TV online. You can also set the recurring payment mode to pay every month without having to repeat this process.</p><p style=\"color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-family: Cambria; font-size: 18px;\">This concludes the article on Comcast Bill Pay. We have not come to the conclusion yet, and I believe you have understood this simple process. If you have any doubt, make sure you reach us at Comcast Help.</p><h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"font-size: 20px; color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-family: Cambria;\">How can I pay my Comcast bill?</h4><p style=\"color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-family: Cambria; font-size: 18px;\">Comcast publicized a new payment option for customers who prefer to pay bill cash for their TV, Internet or phone bills. 7,700 participating 7-Eleven stores. Combined with more than 500 XFINITY stores, Comcast customers have access to over 8,000 cash payment points across the country.</p><p style=\"color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-family: Cambria; font-size: 18px;\">With most 7-Eleven stores open 24 hours a day, seven days a week, paying customers have the ability to pay their bills around the clock, near their home. A list of the participating 7-Eleven stores can be found here.</p><p style=\"color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-family: Cambria; font-size: 18px;\"><strong>How it works:</strong></p><ol type=\"1\" style=\"color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-family: Cambria; font-size: 18px;\"><li>In the XFINITY My Account app, go to the Pay Bill section and select the new option, Cash via PayNearMe.</li><li>Select the amount you want to pay and follow the instructions from PayNearMe until you receive a barcode.</li><li>Visit a participating 7-Eleven store nearby, scan the barcode on your phone and pay the selected amount.</li><li>7-Eleven will send you a paper receipt and you will receive a digital receipt on your phone confirming the payment amount.</li></ol><h5 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"font-size: 19px; color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-family: Cambria;\">How do I check my Comcast bill pay plan?</h5><p style=\"color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-family: Cambria; font-size: 18px;\">Only a registered account user with billing entitlements can access your invoice under My Account. Primary users have full access to view, manage, and pay invoices and can also grant permissions to pay for secondary accounts.</p><p style=\"color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-family: Cambria; font-size: 18px;\">For more information about sharing access to billing amounts for a secondary user, see the instructions for setting the permissions for the secondary Xfinity user name.</p><h5 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"font-size: 19px; color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-family: Cambria;\">How to check your current Comcast bill payment</h5><ol type=\"1\" style=\"color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-family: Cambria; font-size: 18px;\"><li>Log in to “My Account” with a primary user account or a secondary user account with invoice eligibility.</li><li>Click View Billing Details to open a PDF of your most recent invoice in a new tab.</li><li>Billing Summary page – The View Billing Details button is in the center left</li></ol><h5 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"font-size: 19px; color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-family: Cambria;\">How do I view my Comcast payment history?</h5><p style=\"color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-family: Cambria; font-size: 18px;\">You can view your last 24 monthly statements online at any time.</p><ol type=\"1\" style=\"color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-family: Cambria; font-size: 18px;\"><li>Log in to “<strong>My Account</strong>” with a primary user account or a secondary user account with invoice eligibility.</li><li>Click View PDF to open a billing summary on a new tab.</li></ol><h6 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-family: Cambria;\">How to pay Comcast bill by customer service?</h6><p style=\"color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-family: Cambria; font-size: 18px;\">Paying your Xfinity bill is easy in many ways to access and pay for your account. To pay your Xfinity bill, you can:</p><ul style=\"color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-family: Cambria; font-size: 18px;\"><li>Call 1-800-Comcast (1.800.934.6489) to pay your Comcast bill by customer service number.</li><li>To make online comcast payments, visit www.xfinity.com</li><li>Download Xfinity My Account App to pay Xfinity via mobile</li><li>Visit an Comcast location using the Xfinity store locator to pay your comcast bill personally.</li><li>Set up a live chat to walk an agent through the Xfinity bill payment process</li></ul><h6 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-family: Cambria;\">Comcast launches Apple Pay option for Comcast bill payments with Xfinity invoices</h6><p style=\"color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-family: Cambria; font-size: 18px;\">Comcast has updated its Comcast Bill Pay account management app so that Apple Payments can soon accept payments.</p><p style=\"color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-family: Cambria; font-size: 18px;\">According to Comto, the new payment solution for Apple Pay Bill will be introduced in the coming weeks, according to 9to5Mac. Version 1.24.0 of the Comcast My Account app for the iPhone of the cable company contains the new feature.</p><p style=\"color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-family: Cambria; font-size: 18px;\">Comcast customers can easily and securely pay for their cable and Internet bills with Touch ID and Tokenization through Apple Pay instead of entering and saving credit card information online or sending payments by check.</p><p style=\"color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-family: Cambria; font-size: 18px;\">The push notification have been introduced or added to the app for techETA which lets you know the location of your tech along with other minor improvements or enhancements and bug fixes.</p><h6 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-family: Cambria;\">Payment methods for Comcast Bill Payment</h6><p style=\"color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-family: Cambria; font-size: 18px;\">Next, you should choose a payment method to make invoice payments online. There are two options available.</p><ul style=\"color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-family: Cambria; font-size: 18px;\"><li>Checking account / savings account</li><li>Credit / debit cards</li></ul><p style=\"color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-family: Cambria; font-size: 18px;\">Select the payment method you want to use to pay for Comcast invoices. Some details such as bank account number, bank sort code, credit / debit card details, etc. must be filled out.</p><p style=\"color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-family: Cambria; font-size: 18px;\"><strong>Final words</strong></p><p style=\"color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-family: Cambria; font-size: 18px;\">You can also set up automatic bill payments for payments made directly from your bank account. Adding to automatic bill payment may qualify you for an exemption from your monthly Xfinity bill. You can also call us if needed&nbsp;<a href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20231001042546/https://teqsman.com/outage/comcast-internet/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" style=\"color: rgb(84, 190, 115);\">Comcast outage map</a>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<a href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20231001042546/https://www.itforsoftware.com/comcast-email-settings/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" style=\"color: rgb(84, 190, 115);\">Comcast email settings</a><strong>.</strong></p>', 'https://www.teqsman.com/storage/app/public/blog_images/DfycfhsEnuqTuisr7LKaLfa05obojhEZy6dFKq8b.webp', NULL, 'bill-pay', 'Ethan Dolan', '2024-09-17 12:41:01', '2024-09-17 12:41:01');
