ment, especially if you have a credit union. Many credit unions have a clear account of numbering systems.</p><p style=\"color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-family: Assistant;\">According to the municipal ordinance, a withdrawal fee of $ 25 will be charged for any payment that cannot be completed.</p><h5 style=\"font-size: 19px; color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-family: Assistant;\">Where can I pay my charter bill?</h5><p style=\"color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-family: Assistant;\">We are pleased to announce the launch of a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20230325101247/http://teqsman.com/bill-pay/charter/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" style=\"color: rgb(84, 190, 115);\">new charter billing</a>&nbsp;and payment portal that provides you with the highest level of security for your financial information, more payment options, and better customer experience.</p><p style=\"color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-family: Assistant;\">You also have the option of paying your water or tax bills at the counter, by post, telephone, or online. Payment by e-check is still free and a 2.8% service charge (minimum $ 1.50) will be charged for credit card payments.</p><h5 style=\"font-size: 19px; color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-family: Assistant;\">How do I pay my charter bill online?</h5><p style=\"color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-family: Assistant;\">Pay on Spectrum.net</p><ol type=\"1\" style=\"color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-family: Assistant;\"><li>Log in with a master or administrator account.</li><li>Find the invoice section. Select “Make a payment” or “Pay by invoice”.</li><li>Enter your payment information. Payment methods include:</li></ol><ul type=\"1\" style=\"color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-family: Assistant;\"><li>Current or savings account</li><li>Debit card</li><li>Credit card</li></ul><p style=\"color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-family: Assistant;\"><strong>Follow the instructions and make your payment.</strong></p><p style=\"color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-family: Assistant;\">You can choose whether you want to make a single or recurring payment (automatic payment).</p><p style=\"color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-family: Assistant;\"><strong>Note:</strong>&nbsp;Payment details is available at spectrum main website for future for every customer service.</p><h5 style=\"font-size: 19px; color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-family: Assistant;\">Pay the Charter bill via my spectrum application</h5><p style=\"color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-family: Assistant;\">Online Payment for spectrum services is done by My Spectrum app on devices like Android, iphone which can be downloaded from Playstore.</p><ol type=\"1\" style=\"color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-family: Assistant;\"><li>Log into the My Spectrum app with your Spectrum username and password. If you don’t already have one, learn how to create a username.</li><li>Choose the Billing tab.</li><li>Press the Make Payment button.</li><li>Here you can adjust the amount of payment, the date of payment, and the method of payment. Tap the field you want to customise.</li><li>Once you’ve verified that all of the payment information is correct, tap Make a payment. You will receive a confirmation message.</li></ol><h5 style=\"font-size: 19px; color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-family: Assistant;\">Can I pay my Charter bill over the phone?</h5><p style=\"color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-family: Assistant;\">Yes, you can also pay your Spectrum bill over the phone. Just call the spectrum at their payphone number. With the automated spectrum service, you can pay your bill over the phone. As we know bill for Spectrum services is paid online by My Spectrum app on their mobile. Payment is done by the bank accounts registered with the phone number through which app is accessed.</p><h6 style=\"font-size: 18px; color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-family: Assistant;\">Charter bill payments over the phone</h6><p style=\"color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-family: Assistant;\">If you want to choose a replacement internet or television provider, customers must be in